version_description:
- Fixed an issue when opening in FileApp would fail if the app wasn't running in the background
- Fixed iPhone 6 Plus landscape mode crashes
- Other minor fixes

What's new?
- Added support for 3D Touch Quick Actions ( iPhone 6s and 6s Plus )
- Added support for 3D Touch Peek and Pop ( iPhone 6s and 6s Plus )
- Added support for iOS 9 Multitasking ( iPad )
- Updated PDF Component
